            <h1>Twenty-first century global glacier evolution under CMIP6 scenarios and the role of glacier-specific observations</h1>
            <div class="auto-fixed-top-forced article-title">
                <div class="grid-container show-on-fixed" style="display: none">
                    <div class="grid-85 mobile-grid-85 tablet-grid-85 grid-parent">
                        <span class="d-block hide-on-mobile hide-on-tablet journal-contentHeaderColor">Twenty-first century global glacier evolution under CMIP6 scenarios and the role of glacier-specific observations</span>
                        <span class="d-block hide-on-desktop journal-contentHeaderColor">Twenty-first century global glacier evolution under CMIP6 scenarios and the role of...</span>

                        <span>Harry Zekollari et al.</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="grid-1 mobile-grid-15 tablet-grid-15 grid-parent text-right">
                        <a id="scrolltop" class="scrollto" href="https://tc.copernicus.org/articles/18/5045/2024/#top"><i
                                class="co-home"></i> </a>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

                <div class="mb-3 authors-with-affiliations">
                    <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907721">Harry Zekollari<a href="mailto:zharry@ethz.ch"><i class="fal fa-envelope ml-1"></i></a></span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907722">Matthias Huss</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907723">Lilian Schuster</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907724">Fabien Maussion</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907725">David R. Rounce</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907726">Rodrigo Aguayo</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907727">Nicolas Champollion</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907728">Loris Compagno</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907729">Romain Hugonnet</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907730">Ben Marzeion</span>,</nobr> <nobr><span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
                    data-target=".author907731">Seyedhamidreza Mojtabavi</span>,</nobr> <nobr>and <span class="hover-cursor-pointer journal-contentLinkColor hover-underline" data-toggle="modal" 
